&lt;li&gt;Manage platform health across production and sandbox environments, including configuration, customization governance, SuiteCloud+ usage, and oversight.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive adoption and optimization of licensed modules including SuiteAnalytics Connect and SuiteCloud Plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead planning and execution for NetSuite bi-annual releases: assess new functionality, develop test plans, coordinate UAT with business stakeholders, and manage sandbox-to-production promotion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
